description:
A generic iron gauntlet. Fairly heavy, but fits onto
your offhand like a glove (duh).
name: Gauntlet

description: A plain wooden buckler. Good at parrying incoming frontal-attacks.
name: Buckler

description:
A red emblazoned circular guard.
Guarding with this will retaliate with fireballs.
name: Fire Guard

description:
Sacrifice the protectiveness of a shield or gauntlet for
a book that bestows the "fireball" skill!
name: Book of Fireball

description:
A dangerous shield, bestowed with the power of gigashock.
Guarding with this will retaliate with gigashocks.
name: Giga Shield

description:
This outfit looks surprisingly like a certain popular
franchise that starts with ZELD-...
name: Cloth Tunic

description:
A cape that brings with it exceptional MP regeneration!
Equip this when you expect to be casting spells a lot!
name: Cape of the Magus

description:
A dark garb that brings with it an excessive amount of
TP regeneration! Wear this when you want to use skills often!
name: Ninja Garb

description:
A nice set of leather boots for dashing straight forward.
Grants the "Lunge" skill.
name: Shoes of Lunging

description:
A nice set of leather boots for quickly stepping backwards.
Grants the "Backstep" mobility skill.
name: Boots of Backstep

description:
A pair of anklets that enable ultra-precise mobility.
Grants the "Tumble" mobility skill.
name: Anklets of Tumbling

description:
Bestows the "Sonic Wave" ability.
Fires a huge blast of power forward that hits many times.
name: Rune: Sonic Wave

description:
Bestows the "Spike Ball" ability.
Fires a slow-moving ball that deals light damage rapidly.
name: Rune: Spike Ball

description:
Bestows the "Giga Shock" ability.
Shoot to win.
name: Rune: Giga Shock

description:
Bestows the "Poison Fang" ability.
The "poison" state reduces hp over time.
name: Rune: Poison Fang

description:
Bestows the "Disabling Burst" ability.
The "disabled" state prevents basic attacks (allows skill usage).
name: Rune: Disabling Burst

description:
Bestows the "Muted Shot" ability.
The "muted" state prevents skill usage (allows basic attacks).
name: Rune: Muted Shot

description:
Bestows the "Rooting Tendrils" ability.
The "rooted" state prevents movement (allows action).
name: Rune: Rooting Tendrils

description:
Bestows the "Paralysis Stab" ability.
The "paralyzed" state prevents all movement and actions.
name: Rune: Paralysis Stab

description:
Grants +50/hp5.
"hp5" is the amount of hp recovered per 5 seconds.
name: Orb of Life

description:
Grants +50/mp5.
"mp5" is the amount of mp recovered per 5 seconds.
name: Orb of Magi

description:
Grants +50/tp5.
"tp5" is the amount of tp recovered per 5 seconds.
name: Orb of Tech
